@startuml specialist_doctor_sequence
!theme plain
title Specialist Doctor Sequence Diagram - X-ray Management & Results Review

actor "Specialist Doctor" as sd
participant "System" as sys
participant "Database" as db
participant "Notification" as notif

== Login ==
sd -> sys: Login
sys -> db: Validate Credentials
db -> sys: Return User Data
sys -> sd: Display Dashboard

== View Referred Patients ==
sd -> sys: View Referred Patients
sys -> db: Query Patients (referred_to=doctor_id, status='referred')
db -> sys: Return Patient List
sys -> sd: Display Referred Patients

== Create X-ray Request ==
sd -> sys: Select Patient for X-ray Request
sys -> db: Query Patient Details
db -> sys: Return Patient Data
sys -> sd: Display Patient Information

sd -> sys: Create X-ray Request
sd -> sys: Enter Request Details
sys -> sys: Generate Request ID
sys -> db: Insert X-ray Request Record
sys -> db: Update Patient Status to 'xray_requested'
db -> sys: Return Request ID
sys -> notif: Notify X-ray Technicians
sys -> sd: Request Created Successfully

== View Request History ==
sd -> sys: View X-ray Request History
sys -> db: Query Doctor's Requests with Results
db -> sys: Return Request List with Predictions
sys -> sd: Display Request History with Status

== Review X-ray Results ==
sd -> sys: Select Completed Request
sys -> db: Query Prediction Details
db -> sys: Return AI Analysis (prediction, confidence)
sys -> sd: Display Detailed Results

sd -> sys: Review AI Prediction
alt Positive Result
  sys -> sd: Display "Positive for Cardiomegaly" + Confidence
else Negative Result
  sys -> sd: Display "Negative" + Confidence
end

== Create Additional X-ray Request ==
sd -> sys: Request Another X-ray
sys -> db: Create New X-ray Request
db -> sys: Confirm Creation
sys -> notif: Notify Technicians
sys -> sd: New Request Created

== Receive Notifications ==
notif -> sd: Patient Referred to You
notif -> sd: X-ray Result Ready

@enduml